OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny spells and isolated
OL,6,Fshowers, these most likely across the
OL,7,FPennines, until late afternoon. Then
OL,8,Ffrequent showers will spread east,
OL,9,Flocally heavy with a small chance of
OL,10,Fhail and thunder.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FHeavy showers will gradually
OL,13,Fease during the evening becoming light
OL,14,Fand isolated, with some breaks
OL,15,Fdeveloping in the cloud and feeling
OL,16,Fcold. The winds become light and
OL,17,Fvariable.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
