OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FSunshine and isolated heavy
OL,6,Fshowers some of which could be
OL,7,Fthundery. Clouding over from the west
OL,8,Fas rain and strong winds arrive
OL,9,Fovernight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FTuesday breezy with frequent heavy
OL,13,Fshowers. Wednesday breezy with showers
OL,14,For longer spells of rain. Becoming
OL,15,Fsettled and dry on Thursday.
OL,16,FTemperatures near average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
